{"tid":1728820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大J：Ming仔，正所謂，唔出聲無人話你係啞。","createTime":"2019-11-17T04:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T05:56:31.000Z","uid":28114,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"47f79dfabc1a94fefa8f82550899ca1feea225d8","tid":1728820,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:35:54.000Z","msg":"Ming仔，正所謂，唔出聲無人話你係啞。係要衝出黎柒，成個直播都唔知個目的係乜。扮中立又扮唔到，黃你又唔係。<br />\n老實講你公開話自己係藍絲撐警可能仲多財路。<br />\n<br />\n本來以爲你係聰明仔，點知原來只係一名無腦無公關無口才，純發明星夢既撚屌。不過都離地都好多年喇，係時候降落返地面。<br />\n<br />\n不過呢，大家都講夠喇，呢D人由佢自己去擁抱大灣區啦。<br />\n<br />\n理大同學而家水深火熱... 諗下有咩可以做到好過....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/499883930075999/posts/2759240474140322?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F499883930075999%2Fposts%2F2759240474140322%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=ea35557f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/499883930075999/posts/2759240474140322?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"8470cf0aa1f6a3c0642eafae4d451efeb92b3bbc","tid":1728820,"uid":27664,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:37:54.000Z","msg":"On9 Ming佢係配合昨天藍屍齊齊行動啫"},{"pid":"bfea072090a8d03599a27c190dc86eaaa58ddfd4","tid":1728820,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"他們在打的是「<strong>中共政權保衛戰</strong>」，而你們僅僅是在打「<strong>香港生活方式保衛戰</strong>」<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，第一就是分化，把勇武派、和理非派拆分，第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能，坦白說，還是太嫩。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是北京要製造的焦點轉移。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂。</span>"},{"pid":"0209b6f62b1c43fb855f4a0b9c97d1731d5db4dd","tid":1728820,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:40:14.000Z","msg":"ming仔表示仲睇緊留言 扮話好多睇唔切 乜都無答"},{"pid":"f0cfe8f1d33f49e536405f82e61b570878cefc8a","tid":1728820,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:41:49.000Z","msg":"特登琴日出黎柒 應該係想淡化出老解"},{"pid":"dd44f790e2989aaff5b315d89c61470373fa86e5","tid":1728820,"uid":60815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddcd3a5f20f1635212a4d84c2eafa68fccf2ea5e","tid":1728820,"uid":108269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:43:26.000Z","msg":"佢咁都唔做仲好"},{"pid":"be73f7bb88ccf58488817801ebda558439f40edf","tid":1728820,"uid":311279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:44:25.000Z","msg":"【法律撚請入】基本法第十八條=出動老解無違反憲法？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728776\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728776</a><br />\n救救文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9ba9d4df0deb37a7fbcfcddc545f94d7988cc0","tid":1728820,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:44:32.000Z","msg":"迖都冇乜出聲喎 <br />\n只係一直關注<br />\n都變成地底泥"},{"pi